{"tid":1776004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍文理書院「香港校长怒夺学生港独旗帜」","createTime":"2019-12-09T08:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T08:44:25.000Z","uid":281159,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"30910aa3a521d199f51b02d3106d42f3eeb34d5d","tid":1776004,"uid":281159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:20:25.000Z","msg":"【香港學生校運會上舉「港獨」旗 校長震怒衝到賽道奪走旗幟[怒]】#香港校長怒奪學生港獨旗幟# 近日，香港九龍城文理書院一名學生在該校舉辦陸運會時，無視法紀，公然手持寫有政治標語的「港獨」旗幟上場，校長歐陽惠賢大發雷霆並衝到賽道從該生手中奪走旗幟<br />\n<br />\n上埋微博熱搜排13<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Sc095uA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSc095uA.png&h=56a7aa18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YmQNR9A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYmQNR9A.png&h=1105f43e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/600uk2W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F600uk2W.png&h=91317b52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfqVgBh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfqVgBh.png&h=2b468d62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d8cae20a32aa064ea9e25bb7795ff6de7eaf03a","tid":1776004,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T08:44:25.000Z","msg":"don't make stupid people famous"}]}